properties.description: 32-in Stainless Steel and Black Barrel Charcoal Grill
properties.full_description: Cooking with charcoal is now stylish and functional with this dual chamber, stainless Dyna-Glo charcoal grill. The removable steel firebox divider allows for expanding or dividing the cooking space depending on the amount and type of food and total number of people. The two charcoal trays adjust separately to provide flexibility with cooking temperature when different foods require different temperatures at the same time. The lid and front firebox are double-walled to minimize heat loss and improve the burn efficiency of charcoal. The high capacity ash pan is removable for quick and easy clean-up.

properties.description: Portable Tabletop Charcoal Grill and Side Firebox
properties.full_description: Expand your outdoor cooking horizons with the Dyna-Glo portable tabletop charcoal grill and side firebox. This grills portability allows you to grill on the go, whether tailgating, camping or in the backyard. This grill is equipped with a removable charcoal grate and ash pan, which offers easy access to fuel and quick disposal of ash. The porcelain enameled steel cooking grates allow for maximum heat transfer and searing. The Dyna-Glo portable tabletop charcoal grill and side firebox can easily be attached to an existing Dyna-Glo Signature Series barrel grill for horizontal smoking and 287 square inches of extra grilling space. Mounts as an offset smoker box on Dyna-Glo Signature Series charcoal grill models DGSS443CB-D and DGSS675CB-D (sold separately).

properties.full_description: The Regal Pellet 500 grill is a powerful and innovative pellet grill that uses a Wifi and Bluetooth® enabled digital controller to provide enhanced temperature control allowing you to do anything with this grill including low-and-slow smoking at 225°F, roasting at 350°F, or even high-heat searing 600°F.. This pellet grill comes fully equipped with a powerful auger, 22-lb capacity pellet hopper, removable grease management system, unique ash management system, deluxe rotisserie kit, 2 electronic meat probes, base storage and side shelf, and heavy duty and reversible cast iron cooking grids. Total cooking space on this grill is 865 sq. in. including a porcelain coated warming rack.
